KAFKA install:
$ helm repo add bitnami https://charts.bitnami.com/bitnami
$ helm install kafka-release bitnami/kafka

PERSON-SERVICE
Go to modules/01-person-service
$ kubectl apply -f deployment/
$ sh scripts/run_db_command.sh

CONNECTION-SERVICE
Go to modules/02-connection-service
$ kubectl apply -f deployment/
$ sh scripts/run_db_command.sh

LOCATION-SERVER
Go to modules/03-location-server
$ kubectl apply -f deployment/

LOCATION-add
Go to modules/04-location-add
$ kubectl apply -f deployment/

FRONTEND
$ kubectl apply -f deployment/